Sheroo Dara Keeka (11 Septemba 1921 14 Septemba 2006) bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị a mụrụ na India na Tanganyika
N'afọ 1955, ọ bụ otu n'ime ụmụ nwanyị atọ mbụ a họpụtara na Kansụl Iwu.
A mụrụ ya na India n'afọ 1921, Keeka gara St
Xavier's College na Bombay. Ọ kwagara Tanganyika, wee bụrụ onyeisi ụlọ akwụkwọ Aga Khan Girls School na Dodoma n'afọ 1940, ọrụ ọ rụrụ ruo afọ 1944
N'afọ 1953, ọ ghọrọ onye isi oche nke alaka Dodoma nke Tanganyika Society for Prevention of Cruelty to Animals. Di ya Dara Framroze Keeka, onye gụsịrị akwụkwọ na St
Xavier's College, bụ onye ọka iwu a ma ama na onyeisi oche nke Dodoma Town Council.

N'afọ 1955, a họpụtara ya na Kansụl Iwu na-anọchite anya Central Province dị ka otu n'ime ụmụ nwanyị atọ mbụ, na-eje ozi ruo n'afọ 1958. O mechara mee mkpọsa maka 'Votes for Married Women', ma jee ozi dị ka onyeisi oche nke alaka Dodoma nke Tanganyika Council of Women site n'afọ 1958 ruo afọ 1962. Ọ bụkwa onye kọmishọna Girl Guides site n'afọ 1960 na onye otu kọmitii nke alaka Dodoma nke Tanganyika Red Cross.
